Package tuition

Class Roster

  • java.lang.Object
    • tuition.Roster
  • public class Roster
extends java.lang.Object
    Collects and manages Student objects in roster array. Perform functions called by TuitionManager class. Functions include adding and removing Student objects from the array, and printing the array roster in no specified order, by student major, and or by student standing
    Author:
    Sharukh Khan, Hamad Naveed
